                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18231022-28-off152 t18231022-28-cd153"></join>, a shirt, value 3 s.; a pair of trowsers, value 2 s.; two pairs of stockings, value 2 s., and a pair of shoes, value 2 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18231022-28-victim303" type="victimName">
